{"tid":1616632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記協就警方阻礙採訪及向記者使用過度武力申請司法覆核","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T13:56:54.000Z","uid":32577,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5e3501b768c3f9a06652668095641df7352b95","tid":1616632,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"香港記者協會表示，今日下午就警方未能履行憲制責任及通例的要求配合傳媒採訪，甚至妨礙傳媒採訪，以及向記者使用過度武力，入稟法院，申請司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n記協表示，自6月中的示威活動開始以來，警方一直對記者採取妨礙採訪的策略，施以不必要及過度的武力，過去三個多月，記協發出多份聲明、信函及向監警會投訴，惟警務處處長及政府均未能採取有效措施改善。記協為此向法庭申請司法覆核，期望高等法院能宣布警方非法妨礙記者採訪及對記者使用過度武力，警方和政府均有責任保障新聞自由及調查對警隊的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n記協表示，是次司法覆核以多個記者親身經歷的個案展示過去幾個月來，警方的失誤以及對記者的不當行為氾濫，包括對記者使用辱罵及侮辱性言辭、使用高強度燈光和頻閃燈光干擾攝錄設備、無理驅趕記者、故意遮擋記者視線導致記者無法採訪、故意不出示警察委任證或警員編號，亦有記者被毆打、被腳踢、遭噴射胡椒噴霧，有警員瞄準記者發射催淚彈及向記者投擲催淚彈，利用水炮車對準記者發射，甚至使用橡膠子彈及布袋彈射向記者。<br />\n<br />\n記協主席楊健興表示，堅信言論自由和新聞自由是香港重要的基石，必須守護，期待法院發揮監察作用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484096-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484096-20191003.htm&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=e0f9fe53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484096-20191003.htm&h=50af01c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484096-20191003.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e4ca94635158055c31d527cfa07cb988dd037cd5","tid":1616632,"uid":261180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:23:01.000Z","msg":"美國手足致Pelosi書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614231</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1cad33828f2b2828bb970b27c35bdaffe660338","tid":1616632,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"2a5a4ec5a764c1406e3b9e49fc6020f94674923a","tid":1616632,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d4aa5305308c002b1d94df205eb805f1c966c068","tid":1616632,"uid":213597,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc639de2b7dd0457320a0d999f31132b4f6df082","tid":1616632,"uid":213597,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c38da0078e2ddb1ed9f5d949499c2b2b2e29da1e","tid":1616632,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79637d6ce876dbfa5c98eb12c769b894e3dc7185","tid":1616632,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=bca05673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"99038c533ffb60311886a5a890fa204f238efcba","tid":1616632,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"終於出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多多錢都捐"},{"pid":"98aa68b671013616755c0c9c8a4a08e613a316bc","tid":1616632,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"終於做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}